her? Well, we&#039;ll just say Brae had decided to take one for the team and stay outta the whole thing. Just like he was doin today, workin in the yard, preparin the seeds for the comin spring.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421216297";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffc400";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14212162830";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff8c00";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1206212;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1206212";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"21";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"45";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Jessamine";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"341";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:443:"Of course Jessamine wouldn&#039;t have that. If her plan was to succeed, she&#039;d need to draw Braeburn in closer! So, with a bit of tweaking and a well placed word or two...she&#039;d make a messenger out of one of her would-be admirers. The stallion galloped at full speed toward Braeburn&#039;s homestead and once he&#039;d got there, he propped his front legs over the fence. &quot;Hey Braeburn!&quot; He called at the top of his voice. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421216759";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cdc41d";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14212167773";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#14b05f";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1206213;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1206213";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"21";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:8:"Braeburn";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"596";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:125:"/me stops and turns with a smile. &quot;Well, howdy do there Cuz! What can ah do for ya on this beeeaaayuuuuutiful day?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421216994";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffc400";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14212169800";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff8c00";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1206214;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1206214";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"21";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"45";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Jessamine";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"341";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:296:"&quot;Ain&#039;t got tah&#039;m fer&#039; talkin&#039; bout the weather, cuz. That mare, the one that&#039; all the guys are&#039; talkin&#039; &#039;bout? She&#039;s havin&#039; some kind of concert! Reckon&#039; we aught t&#039; go?&quot; The stallion was practically bouncing with excitement. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421217113";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cdc41d";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14212171320";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#14b05f";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1206215;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1206215";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"21";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:8:"Braeburn";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"596";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:77:"&quot;Concert?&quot; Braeburn cocks his head. &quot;What kinda concert?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421217381";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffc400";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14212173665";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff8c00";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1206216;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1206216";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"21";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"45";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Jessamine";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"341";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:150:"&quot;Ah&#039; suppose she&#039;s gonna&#039; sang&#039;&quot; The stallion scratched his head with a hoof, making sure to fix his stetson afterward. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421217447";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cdc41d";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14212174654";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#14b05f";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1206217;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1206217";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"21";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:8:"Braeburn";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"596";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:90:"&quot;Well, now, that sounds mahty pretty. S&#039;pose we&#039;ll head on over then.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421217498";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffc400";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14212174839";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff8c00";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1206221;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1206221";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"21";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"45";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Jessamine";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"341";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:301:"The stallion nodded his head excitedly and slipped his front legs off the fence. Meanwhile, a small stage had been set up in Appleloosa&#039;s town square, the curtains were currently drawn...but a small crowd of ponies, a majority of them being stallions, had gathered to wait for the show to start. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421217764";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cdc41d";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14212177822";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#14b05f";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1206233;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1206233";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"21";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:8:"Braeburn";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"596";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:292:"/me and cousin Blue Skies entered the area from the North and slowly moved among the gathered ponies. &quot;Well now, looks like th&#039; whole town dun showed up,&quot; Brae observes. Though given the general lack of entertainment they didnt&#039; provide themselves, this was pretty normal.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421218024";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffc400";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14212180093";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff8c00";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1206246;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1206246";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"21";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"45";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Jessamine";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"341";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:523:"No sooner had Braeburn and his cousin arrived, the curtains pulled back and a lively melody was played by a piano pony just in front of the stage. Jessamine made her way out to the sound of cheers and whistles. She was dressed in a very frilly bright green bustled gown. Before she began, she made sure to covertly scan over the crowd to make sure her intended guest had arrived. Spotting Braeburn, she smiled and started to sing. &quot;Waaaay out west, in a nest from the rest, dwelt the bestest little Bronco Boy~!&quot; ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421218603";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cdc41d";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14212186217";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#14b05f";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1206248;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1206248";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"21";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:8:"Braeburn";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"596";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:71:"/me smiles broadly, watching the show. &quot;Yeehaw! Sing it gal!&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421218976";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffc400";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14212189617";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff8c00";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1206251;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1206251";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"21";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"45";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Jessamine";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"341";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:414:"&quot;He could ride, he could glide o&#039;er the prairies like an arrow~!&quot; She gestured out over the crowd, pretending to shield her eyes as if looking faraway with a gloved hoof. &quot;Every maid in the glade was afraid he would trade his lil&#039; heart away~!&quot; She placed both hooves over her chest at this point. &quot;So each lil&#039; peach made a nice lil&#039; speech of love t&#039; him~!&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421219238";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cdc41d";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14212192565";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#14b05f";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1206253;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1206253";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"21";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:8:"Braeburn";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"596";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:92:"/me thumps a pony next to him. &quot;Hay, she&#039;s singin &#039;bout you!&quot; and laughs";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421219398";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffc400";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14212193838";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff8c00";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1206263;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1206263";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"21";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"45";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Jessamine";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"341";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:356:"&quot;Pony Boy, Pony Boy, won&#039;t you be my Pony Boy? Don&#039;t say no. Here we go, off across the plains! Marry me, carry me! Right away with you.~ Giddy up, giddy up, giddy up, whoa! My Pony Boy~!&quot; She was joined by a few backup ponies who took their place behind her. As she sang this particular chorus, she happened to lock eyes with Braeburn.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421219561";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cdc41d";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14212195793";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#14b05f";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1206270;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1206270";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"21";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:8:"Braeburn";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"596";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:26:"/me grins and tips his hat";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421219769";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffc400";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14212197543";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff8c00";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1206286;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1206286";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"21";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"45";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Jessamine";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"341";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:533:"After a short instrumental, she began again stepping to one side of the stage. &quot;Till one day, out that way, so they say, came to stay a fluffy ruffle girl.&quot; She fluffed the collar of her gown. &quot;She made eyes, she surprised, and he found his heart was lassoed.~&quot; She bat her eyelashes Braeburn&#039;s way and motioned like she was trying to lasso him. &quot;When he thought he was caught, how he fought, but she taught this pony boy to love.&quot; Mentioning love, she once again placed her hooves over her chest. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421220494";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cdc41d";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14212205132";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#14b05f";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1206290;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1206290";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"21";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:8:"Braeburn";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"596";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:129:"/me laughs and plays along, pretending to be roped. He turns and pretends to be fighting it as he slowly moves towards the stage.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421220785";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffc400";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14212207708";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff8c00";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1206291;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1206291";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"21";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:8:"Braeburn";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"596";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:39:"The ponies nearby laughed at his antics";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421220808";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffc400";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14212207936";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff8c00";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1206294;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1206294";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"21";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"45";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Jessamine";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"341";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:165:"&quot;But he balked when she talked of a trip to Manehattan, so she sang to him!~&quot; The chorus began again and continued to encourage Braeburn&#039;s attention. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421221296";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cdc41d";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14212213150";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#14b05f";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1206296;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1206296";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"21";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:8:"Braeburn";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"596";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:157:"/me waves a dismissive hoof at the mention of Manehattan and starts to strut away, but at the mention of singin, he lets his head be pulled back towards her.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421221523";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffc400";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14212215083";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff8c00";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1206298;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1206298";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"21";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"45";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Jessamine";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"341";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:237:"&quot;Pony Boy, Pony Boy, won&#039;t you be my Pony Boy? Don&#039;t say no. Here we go! Off across the plains.~ Marry me, carry me right away with you. Giddy up, giddy up, giddy up, whoa! My Pony Boy!&quot; They all sang together. &quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421221696";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cdc41d";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14212217149";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#14b05f";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1206299;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1206299";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"21";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:8:"Braeburn";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"596";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:60:"&quot;Yeehaw!&quot; Brae shouts waving his hat at the chorus";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421221821";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffc400";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14212218062";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff8c00";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1206302;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1206302";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"21";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"45";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Jessamine";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"341";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:292:"With that, the song came to a close and it finished with all the singers ending with &quot;My Pony Booy~!&quot; With the performance over, there was a roar of cheers and whistles. Jessamine bowed and since Braeburn was so close...tossed a lace handkerchief to him before the curtains closed. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421222334";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cdc41d";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14212223530";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#14b05f";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1206305;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1206305";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"21";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:8:"Braeburn";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"596";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:213:"/me watched that favor dance in the breeze for a moment before he realized what he was supposed to do with it and caught it just before it hit the ground. He just stands there, staring at it a bit, kinda confused.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421222532";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffc400";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14212225174";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff8c00";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1206306;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1206306";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"21";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"45";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Jessamine";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"341";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:24:"(( I gotta go to bed. ))";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421222605";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cdc41d";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14212226236";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#14b05f";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1206307;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1206307";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"21";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:8:"Braeburn";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"596";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:13:"((  me too ))";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1421222614";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffc400";